      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<a href='/d/aidra-pipeline-metrics' style='text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block;height:100%'>\n  <div style='height:100%;padding:18px 20px;border-radius:12px;background:#111922;border:1px solid #2b3645;transition:all .15s ease'>\n    <div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:start'>\n      <div style='font-size:11px;color:#7ee2a8;letter-spacing:2px;font-weight:700'>02 · PIPELINE METRICS</div>\n      <div style='font-size:13px;color:#84baef'>open →</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style='font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#f3f6fb;margin:8px 0 6px'>Is the system healthy?</div>\n    <div style='font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:#aebed1'>Run rate, inference latency, peak RAM, CPU, error rate and structured logs. Sourced from Prometheus and Loki, scoped to the AIDRA service.</div>\n  </div>\n</a>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": { "x": 16, "y": 18, "w": 8, "h": 6 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<a href='/d/aidra-tipcue-replay' style='text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block;height:100%'>\n  <div style='height:100%;padding:18px 20px;border-radius:12px;background:#111922;border:1px solid #2b3645;transition:all .15s ease'>\n    <div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:start'>\n      <div style='font-size:11px;color:#7ee2a8;letter-spacing:2px;font-weight:700'>09 · TIP &amp; CUE REPLAY</div>\n      <div style='font-size:13px;color:#84baef'>open →</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style='font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#f3f6fb;margin:8px 0 6px'>The satellite chasing its own findings</div>\n    <div style='font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:#aebed1'>Autonomous re-tasking: when AIDRA spots a low-confidence cluster, it queues a re-observation (T0 → Cue → T1) and you can replay the before / after with confidence uplift. SatCen tender extra.</div>\n  </div>\n</a>"
      }
    },

    {
