        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<a href='/d/aidra-orbital-latency' style='text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block;height:100%'>\n  <div style='height:100%;padding:18px 20px;border-radius:12px;background:#111922;border:1px solid #2b3645;transition:all .15s ease'>\n    <div style='display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:start'>\n      <div style='font-size:11px;color:#f3d76b;letter-spacing:2px;font-weight:700'>07 · ORBITAL LATENCY</div>\n      <div style='font-size:13px;color:#84baef'>open →</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style='font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#f3f6fb;margin:8px 0 6px'>Sensor → operator, end to end</div>\n    <div style='font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:#aebed1'>Acquisition, processing, downlink, ground latency — with and without OBDP, broken down per profile. The one chart that justifies the whole project.</div>\n  </div>\n</a>"
